casebody.data:
Excelsior Steam-Power Co., Respondent, v. Marlow, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 19, 1890.) Appeal from second district court.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Campbell & Van Alstine, for appellant. H. Swain, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
